Maintainer: Kendall Weaver <kendall@peppermintos.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5.0.0)
Standards-Version: 3.9.5

Package: peppermint-control-center
Depends: python3, python3-gi, xfwm4, xbindkeys, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: xbindkeys-config
Architecture: all 
Description:  Window manager and input settings for Peppermint OS.
 Application designed to replace several default xfwm4 settings
 applications along with the severely dated mintinput application.
 Additionally this will eventually serve as a complete keyboard
 shortcut manager.
 
